Title: Viseclaw Soup
Description:
Nothing tastes quite like viseclaw soup.  It's a krasarang specialty!

I was just about to start up on a new batch when I realized I am missing a key ingredient, the eyes!

I need you to kill the viseclaw fishers on the beach and return with their eyes for the soup!
ObjectivesText: Kill Viseclaw Fishers on the beach and return with 16 eyes to make some yummy soup.
